channel.title: Unusual Java Error In Compiler
channel.description:
with my compiler i get a random error message
Here's compiler code
@echo off COLOR 08 title BJDJScape Client "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_06\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java pause
And this is the error message
Note: stream.java uses or overrides a deprecated API. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:deprecation for details. Press any key to continue ...
Can someone please help me?
